<section class="page-section">
  <h1 class="section-title">About Tokyo Panel</h1>
  
  <div class="section-content">
    <p>
      Welcome to Tokyo Panel, where fashion meets manga artistry. We create wearable manga panels 
      that bring the dynamic energy and visual storytelling of Japanese comics to your wardrobe.
    </p>
    
    <div class="about-grid mt-lg">
      <div class="about-card">
        <h3>Our Mission</h3>
        <p>
          To bridge the gap between manga culture and streetwear fashion, creating unique pieces 
          that allow you to express your love for manga in style.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="about-card">
        <h3>Our Vision</h3>
        <p>
          To become the leading brand for manga-inspired apparel, bringing the vibrant world 
          of Japanese comics to fashion-forward individuals worldwide.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="about-card">
        <h3>Our Story</h3>
        <p>
          Founded with a passion for both manga and fashion, Tokyo Panel was born from the idea 
          that clothing can be a canvas for storytelling. Each design is carefully crafted to 
          capture the essence of manga panels, creating wearable art that speaks to your style.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-lg">
      <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-manga); font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--glow-primary);">
        Why Choose Tokyo Panel?
      </h2>
      <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0;">
        <li style="margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 2rem; position: relative;">
          <span style="position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--glow-primary); text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--glow-primary);">◆</span>
          Premium quality materials and printing
        </li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 2rem; position: relative;">
          <span style="position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--glow-primary); text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--glow-primary);">◆</span>
          Unique manga-inspired designs
        </li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 2rem; position: relative;">
          <span style="position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--glow-primary); text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--glow-primary);">◆</span>
          Sustainable and ethical production
        </li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 2rem; position: relative;">
          <span style="position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--glow-primary); text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--glow-primary);">◆</span>
          Worldwide shipping available
        </li>
      </ul>
